The,Language,Detection,API,is,a,simple,language,identification,API,that,is,useful,when,dealing,with,texts,and,currently,supports,languages,All,the,requests,must,be,sent,either,by,GET,or,POST,to,the,API,endpoint,and,allows,you,to,define,how,you,send,to,the,text,for,which,you,want,the,language,to,be,recognized,The,Dandelion,API,extracts,meaning,from,unstructured,text,puts,it,in,context,and,provides,Semantic,Text,Analytics,as,a,service,that,includes,text,actionable,data,and,more